    • Uses of Person in FMS.provided

      Subclasses of Person in FMS.provided 
      Modifier and Type Class Description
      class  Passenger
      A passenger in the flight management system (FMS).
      In addition to personal details a passenger stores information which flight he or she boarded, if any.
      class  Staff
      An airline staff member in the flight management system (FMS).
      In addition to person details, each airline staff member has a specific role, including, but not limited to, pilot, stewardess, chef de cabin.
